headline: DexCom Shares May Rise as G7 15-Day CGM System Gets FDA Clearance
summary: DXCM secures FDA clearance for its G7 15-Day CGM, the longest-lasting and most accurate wearable, enhancing user convenience and expanding diabetes care access.

headline: Prada to acquire Versace, CarMax reports mixed Q4 results: Morning Buzz
summary: The major averages were sharply lower near noon, curtailing some of yesterday’s sharp gains after President Donald Trump announced a 90-day pause on some of his “reciprocal” tariffs, despite announcing an increase on the cumulative tariff rate on Chinese imports.
